yingyinNormal.en: This is an impressive list of hobbies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的兴趣爱好可真厉害。

yingyinNormal.en: He is my greatest triumph. So impressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拉拢到他是我最大的胜利。真是叹为观止。

yingyinNormal.en: You have a very impressive resume, Ms. Green.
yingyinNormal.zh: 格林小姐，你的履历非常精彩。

yingyinNormal.en: Impressive. Thank you. Guilty. Pay the cashier.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩服佩服。谢谢。罪名成立，去付钱吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I have to say, the early results are impressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我必须承认前期的成果令人惊叹。

yingyinNormal.en: Very impressive. Just one thing. They're not married.
yingyinNormal.zh: 分析得真到位，除了一件事，他们没有结婚。

yingyinNormal.en: Impressive, stiff. Congrats.
yingyinNormal.zh: 令人刮目相看嘛，灰袍子，恭喜你。

yingyinNormal.en: It's an impressive calling card that can lead to even more impressive bullets in the years ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 正是这张抢眼的名片，可以成就你们的未来之路。

yingyinNormal.en: Impressive. It's like Tony Robbins and a pine nut had a baby.
yingyinNormal.zh: 厉害啊，他就像安东尼·罗宾和一颗松子生的孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it's quite impressive. You had a good eye even back then.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不得不让人赞叹，你那时候就有这么好的眼光。

yingyinNormal.en: That sounds impressive. How do you do that? With big rubber bands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这听上去很不错。是怎么做到的呢？因为这里有弹力绳。

yingyinNormal.en: When it came to holding a grudge, Juli Baker was truly impressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 朱莉·贝克记仇的本事真心让我佩服。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's say for one moment that I can't rationally explain your impressive parlor tricks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就算真是这样，又怎么合理地解释你这金口玉牙的本事。

yingyinNormal.en: You care what she thinks. You maintain an impressive facade. I think it's about to break.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在乎她的想法。你维持了一个了不起的假象。我想就要打破了。

yingyinNormal.en: Last school you went to was Cutler High in Connecticut. Straight-A student. Very impressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 转学前的学校是康涅狄格州的卡特勒高中，高材生，很好。

yingyinNormal.en: I reviewed your impressive transcripts. I expect your light will shine brightly at East High.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看过你优异的成绩单，相信在东高中你也会出类拔萃。

yingyinNormal.en: When I threw up in the pumpkin? More memorable than that. Really? That was pretty impressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我吐在了一个南瓜灯里吗？比那件事更值得记住。真的吗？我觉得刚那件事超屌啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, now, wait a minute, Phoebe told me that you owned your own restaurant. That's impressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，等等，菲比告诉我你是自己开餐厅的，真是了不起。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, please, luck had nothing to do with it. You people need to know how impressive this man is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，这和幸运完全没关系。你们要知道的是他有多厉害。

yingyinNormal.en: But unlike Edison, we've got some very impressive technology these days to help with the search.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但和爱迪生不同的是，如今我们有了很专业的技术以帮助寻找能源。
